title: Stormshield: Gateway status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/stormshield
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check displays the status of a gateway. The state will change to
 {CRIT} if a gateway is down and to {UNKNOWN} if the reported status is
 undefined. Additionally the information about gateway type and the associated
 router is displayed.

item:
 The name of the gateway is the item

inventory:
 One service for each gateway is created
